headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Costco Wholesale (COST) After Strong Multi Year Share Gains
summary: If you have ever looked at Costco Wholesale and wondered whether the current share price still makes sense, this article walks through what the numbers say about value. Costco shares last closed at US$963.61, with returns of 2.2% over 7 days, 12.6% over 30 days, 12.8% year to date, 2.7% over 1 year, 103.8% over 3 years and 181.4% over 5 years, which naturally raises questions about what is already priced in.
